	 Education Center .\n\nEvent Logistics: This group is open to children of 
	all abilities\, ages 0 to 5 years old.\, Kaleidoscope Play & Learn is for 
	Family\, Friend & Neighbor Caregivers\, Parents\, and the children in thei
	r care. This is not a drop-off program and it is not agood fit for daycare
