SUMMARY:Homework Help
DTSTAMP:20260326T010713Z
DTSTART:20260331T223000Z
DESCRIPTION:Tuesday\, March 31\, 2026\, 3:30 - 7:30pm\n\nHomework Help volu
	nteers will be at this branch to assist K-12 students with school assignme
	nts during the school year.\n\nLocation Link:\n\nNorthgate Branch\n\nRoom 
	Location: Meeting Room\n\nRegistration Required: Registration is not requi
	red.\n\nDetailed Description: If you are working on a tough homework assig
